---
title: Tuscan Sausage Linguine with Sweet Bell Pepper and Parmesan
description: Juicy pork sausage and garlic create a savoury flavour base for this classic pasta sauce. Enhanced with sweet peppers, chili and Parmesan cheese, this recipe is so simple and delicious, you'll want it to become a part of your weekly repertoire.
